Term Deposit Prediction & Marketing Analysis

Targeting Customers that are likely to opt into a Term Deposit service

Business Science

2/13/2019

Executive Summary

  • Duration since last contact and success of prior enrollments are correlated to success of Term Deposit opt-in
  • A strategy targeting customers that havent been contacted in 319 days and have those with prior enrollments yields 32% positive outcomes (enrollments) vs 4.3% otherwise.

Analysis

Correlation of various features to Term Deposit enrollment. Duration since last contact and success of prior enrollments are correlated to success of Term Deposit opt-in.

Strategy

A strategy targeting customers that havent been contacted in 319 days and have those with prior enrollments yields 32% positive outcomes (enrollments) vs 4.3% otherwise.
